his be a joint account?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/21.mp3","time_start":52.13,"time_end":54.31},{"position":22,"content":"No, just myself.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/22.mp3","time_start":54.31,"time_end":55.93},{"position":23,"content":"Okay, fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/23.mp3","time_start":55.93,"time_end":57.75},{"position":24,"content":"And where are you living, Mr Henes?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/24.mp3","time_start":57.75,"time_end":59.79},{"position":25,"content":"15, Riverside.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/25.mp3","time_start":59.92,"time_end":61.78},{"position":26,"content":"Is that all one word?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/26.mp3","time_start":61.78,"time_end":63.36},{"position":27,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/27.mp3","time_start":63.36,"time_end":64.17},{"position":28,"content":"Exeter?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/28.mp3","time_start":64.17,"time_end":65.27},{"position":29,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/29.mp3","time_start":65.27,"time_end":66.05},{"position":30,"content":"How long have you been at your present address?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/30.mp3","