content":"Okay. Thank you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/40.mp3","time_start":94.29,"time_end":96.43},{"position":41,"content":"Do you have a daytime telephone number?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/41.mp3","time_start":96.43,"time_end":98.63},{"position":42,"content":"Yes, I think the number at my office is 606295.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/42.mp3","time_start":98.63,"time_end":104.71},{"position":43,"content":"Um, just a minute, I'd better check.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/43.mp3","time_start":104.71,"time_end":107.5},{"position":44,"content":"Oh, no, sorry, 616. I'm not used to it yet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/44.mp3","time_start":107.85,"time_end":112.49},{"position":45,"content":"Would you like my home number too?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/45.mp3","time_start":112.75,"time_end":114.97},{"position":46,"content":"Yes please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/46.mp3","time_start":114.97,"time_end":115.93},{"position":47,"content":"It's 796431.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/47.mp3","time_start":115.93,"time_end":120.15},{"position":48,"content":"Are they both local numbers?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/48.mp3","time_start":120.15,"time_end":122.15},{"position":49,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/49.mp3","time_start":122.15,"time_end":122.98},{"position":50,"content":"Right. And your occupation?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/50.mp3","time_start":123.66,"time_end":127.15},{"position":51,"content":"Well, I'm in Britain as a project manager, but that's not my main job.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/51.mp3","time_start":127.15,"time_end":131.75},{"position":52,"content":"I'm an engineer by profession.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/52.mp3","time_start":131.75,"time_end":133.75},{"position":53,"content":"I see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/53.mp3","time_start":133.75,"time_end":134.47},{"position":54,"content":"I think I'll put that then. It's shorter!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/54.mp3","time_start":134.47,"time_end":137.58},{"position":55,"content":"Now, we usually ask for a piece of information which we can use to check your identity, for security reasons.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/55.mp3","time_start":137.58,"time_end":144.18},{"position":56,"content":"You know, if you phone us.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/56.mp3","time_start":144.18,"time_end":146.07},{"position":57,"content":"Like, erm, my wife's first name?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/57.mp3","time_start":146.07,"time_end":148.41},{"position":58,"content":"Mother's might be better. It's less likely to be known.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/58.mp3","time_start":148.41,"time_end":152.0},{"position":59,"content":"Okay. Hers is Siti.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/59.mp3","time_start":152.0,"time_end":154.06},{"position":60,"content":"Siti?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/60.mp3","time_start":154.06,"time_end":154.89},{"position":61,"content":"Yes, SITI.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/61.mp3","time_start":154.89,"time_end":157.76},{"position":62,"content":"It's Indonesian.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/62.mp3","time_start":157.76,"time_end":159.09},{"position":63,"content":"Fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/63.mp3","time_start":159.09,"time_end":160.21},{"position":64,"content":"And how much would you like to open your account with?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/64.mp3","time_start":160.21,"time_end":162.85},{"position":65,"content":"We usually ask for a minimum sum of £50.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/65.mp3","time_start":162.85,"time_end":165.79},{"position":66,"content":"That's about €75.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/66.mp3","time_start":165.79,"time_end":167.9},{"position":67,"content":"Well, I'm going to transfer €2,000 from my Dutch account, just till I get paid.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/67.mp3","time_start":168.03,"time_end":173.79},{"position":68,"content":"In fact, I wanted to ask you about that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/68.mp3","time_start":173.92,"time_end":176.71},{"position":69,"content":"What's the best way to do it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/69.mp3","time_start":176.71,"time_end":178.51},{"position":70,"content":"It depends which bank you're with.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/70.mp3","time_start":178.51,"time_end":180.67},{"position":71,"content":"It's the Fransen Bank in Utrecht.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/71.mp3","time_start":180.67,"time_end":183.13},{"position":72,"content":"OK, fine. I'll check that in a minute.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/72.mp3","time_start":183.13,"time_end":185.73},{"position":73,"content":"If we have links with them we can do a direct transfer. But it's not a big problem either way.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/73.mp3","time_start":185.73,"time_end":190.42},{"position":74,"content":"Um, let's see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/74.mp3","time_start":190.62,"time_end":192.7},{"position":75,"content":"How often would you like to receive statements?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/75.mp3","time_start":192.7,"time_end":195.23},{"position":76,"content":"I haven't really thought.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/76.mp3","time_start":195.75,"time_end":197.5},{"position":77,"content":"What's the usual thing?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/77.mp3","time_start":197.5,"time_end":198.96},{"position":78,"content":"It's up to you. Some people like them weekly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/78.mp3","time_start":198.96,"time_end":201.5},{"position":79,"content":"Oh, no, that's too often.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/79.mp3","time_start":201.5,"time_end":203.41},{"position":80,"content":"Can I have them sent, um, once a month?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/80.mp3","time_start":203.41,"time_end":206.22},{"position":81,"content":"Yes, that's fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/81.mp3","time_start":206.22,"time_end":207.46},{"position":82,"content":"Is there anything else?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/82.mp3","time_start":207.74,"time_end":209.2},{"position":83,"content":"I was thinking of registering for your internet service at some stage.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/83.mp3","time_start":209.45,"time_end":213.44},{"position":84,"content":"Oh, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/84.mp3","time_start":213.44,"time_end":214.09},{"position":85,"content":"Would you like me to send you information about that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/85.mp3","time_start":214.09,"time_end":216.99},{"position":86,"content":"Please, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/86.mp3","time_start":216.99,"time_end":218.13},{"position":87,"content":"And would you like to receive information about the bank's other services -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/87.mp3","time_start":218.13,"time_end":221.66},{"position":88,"content":"insurance, loans, anything like that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/88.mp3","time_start":221.66,"time_end":224.71},{"position":89,"content":"Hmm, I don't think so, thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/89.mp3","time_start":224.71,"time_end":226.83},{"position":90,"content":"That's okay then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/90.mp3","time_start":226.83,"time_end":228.17},{"position":91,"content":"And one last thing, if you agree...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-6-test-3-part-1-2023-08-02-10-56-41/91.mp3","time_start":228.37,"time_end":231.11}]}